...because you know, they aren't quite as bad as Pero...

625
00:47:50,972 --> 00:47:54,972
...but they can get pretty nasty sometimes!

626
00:47:54,972 --> 00:47:59,672
Mocochyan! You're not going to be rude to our next guest or anything, right?

627
00:47:59,672 --> 00:48:01,972
Especially before calling them out!

628
00:48:01,972 --> 00:48:03,972
We'll see!

629
00:48:03,972 --> 00:48:06,972
Well, let's get them out here then!

630
00:48:06,972 --> 00:48:09,972
Could it be, could it be?!

631
00:48:09,972 --> 00:48:11,472
Okay!

632
00:48:11,472 --> 00:48:14,972
せーの、どうぞー！
On three, please come in!

633
00:48:14,972 --> 00:48:18,672
わわわわ！来たしん！来たしんよ！来たしんよ！
Wa-wa-wa-wa! I'm here! I'm here! I'm here!

634
00:48:18,672 --> 00:48:20,472
あーん、ちゅっ！
Mwah!

635
00:48:20,472 --> 00:48:22,672
きゃあああ！ちゅっちゅ！
Kyaaaa! Mwah mwah!

636
00:48:22,672 --> 00:48:24,972
自己紹介お願いします！
Please introduce yourself!

637
00:48:24,972 --> 00:48:27,972
クロちゃんです！わわわわー！
It's Kuro-chan! Wa-wa-wa-wa!

638
00:48:27,972 --> 00:48:30,972
来たしんよ！
I'm here!

639
00:48:30,972 --> 00:48:33,672
はじめまして！
Nice to meet you!

640
00:48:33,672 --> 00:48:36,472
チワワじゃないよ、フワワだよ！
I'm not a Chihuahua, I'm Fuwawa!

641
00:48:36,472 --> 00:48:39,472
フワワじゃないよ、モココだよ！
I'm not Fuwawa, I'm Mococo!

642
00:48:39,472 --> 00:48:41,272
二人合わせて...
The two of us together...

643
00:48:41,272 --> 00:48:43,672
フワモコです！バウバウ！
We are Fuwamoko! Bau Bau!

644
00:48:43,672 --> 00:48:48,472
よろしくお願いします！
It's a pleasure to meet you!

645
00:48:48,472 --> 00:48:53,472
フワモコのわちゃわちゃバースデーフェスティバルに来てくれてありがとうございます！
Thank you so much for coming to Fuwamoko's chaotic Birthday Festival!

646
00:48:53,472 --> 00:48:57,272
ハッピーバースデーだしんよ、フワモコ！
Happy birthday, Fuwamoko!

647
00:48:57,272 --> 00:48:59,472
ありがとうございます！
Thank you so much!

648
00:48:59,472 --> 00:49:01,472
いいしんね！
Very nice!

649
00:49:01,472 --> 00:49:05,972
