I'm sure there are many Ruffians watching right now, but...

650
00:49:05,972 --> 00:49:09,972
クロちゃんがどんな人なのか説明してもらえますか？
Could you explain what kind of person you are, Kuro-chan?

651
00:49:09,972 --> 00:49:11,972
え？自分ですんの？これ！
Eh? I have to do it myself?

652
00:49:11,972 --> 00:49:13,672
そうです！自己紹介！
Yes! Self-introduction!

653
00:49:13,672 --> 00:49:17,672
わかったしんよ。だってこれ海外の人も見てますもんね？
Understood. Since overseas people are watching too, right?

654
00:49:17,672 --> 00:49:20,972
海外の人もわかる自己紹介しますからね。
I'll do an intro that overseas people can understand.

655
00:49:20,972 --> 00:49:25,972
Nice to meet you, nice to meet you, chu, chu, chu, chu, tulip!

656
00:49:25,972 --> 00:49:31,472
え、困らないで？
Eh, don't look so troubled?

657
00:49:31,472 --> 00:49:33,972
え、クロちゃんは...チューリップ？
Eh, Kuro-chan is... a tulip?

658
00:49:33,972 --> 00:49:35,972
チューリップ？No, no, no, no!
A tulip? No, no, no, no!

659
00:49:35,972 --> 00:49:38,972
ちょっとまだわからないかもしれないから...
Some people might still not understand, so...

660
00:49:38,972 --> 00:49:43,972
えーとね、安田大サーカスっていうトリオを組んでる、えーと、芸人さんで...
Well, I'm a comedian in a trio called Yasuda Dai Circus...

661
00:49:43,972 --> 00:49:48,972
あと豆柴の大群のプロデュースもやってますだし、作詞とかもしてます、クロちゃんです！
And I also produce Mameshiba no Taigun and write lyrics. I'm Kuro-chan!

662
00:49:48,972 --> 00:49:51,272
お、おー！
Oh, wow!

663
00:49:51,272 --> 00:49:53,972
じゃあ今度は英語でお願いします！
Then, this time, please do it in English!

664
00:49:53,972 --> 00:49:54,972
English!

665
00:49:54,972 --> 00:49:55,972
え？僕が？
Eh? Me?

666
00:49:55,972 --> 00:49:57,672
Yes, 自分で！
Yes, yourself!

667
00:49:57,672 --> 00:50:00,672
え、そんなこと急に言われたら、it's shy...
Eh, if you say that so suddenly, I'm shy...

668
00:50:00,672 --> 00:50:02,472
Fuwawa...

669
00:50:01,927 --> 00:50:03,127
言い訳は無し！
No excuses!

670
00:50:03,127 --> 00:50:04,927
聞いてる？人の話
Are you listening to what people say?

671
00:50:04,927 --> 00:50:06,427
頑張って、英語！
Do your best with English!

672
00:50:06,427 --> 00:50:09,727
英語？ええと、なんなんだろうな。ええと...
English? Uh, let me see... what is it...

673
00:50:09,927 --> 00:50:12,427
FuwaMoco comedian!
FuwaMoco comedians!

674
00:50:12,427 --> 00:50:15,927
Idol producer. / いやいや、かっこいい！
Idol producer. / No way, that's cool!

675
00:50:15,927 --> 00:50:18,727
やってるしんよ。 / おお、できる！
I'm doing it-shin! / Oh, you can do it!

676
00:50:18,727 --> 00:50:22,927
クロちゃん、テレビでよく見てるけど...
We watch Kuro-chan on TV a lot, but...

677
