やっぱ照れくさいけど
And it's embarrassing after all

749
00:55:27,248 --> 00:55:33,248
死ぬまで忘れられないチューしよ
Let's share a kiss we'll never forget until we die

750
00:55:33,248 --> 00:55:36,748
いかれた街はゾンビで溢れる
This crazy town is overflowing with zombies

751
00:55:36,748 --> 00:55:39,748
君は僕に恋してる
You are in love with me

752
00:55:39,748 --> 00:55:45,748
ときめく胸につながるロープを引きなよ
Pull the rope connected to your throbbing heart

753
00:55:45,848 --> 00:55:49,548
Bet bet bet on! Bet on chu!

754
00:55:49,548 --> 00:55:52,648
Bet bet bet on! Bet bet bet on! bet on chu!

755
00:55:52,648 --> 00:55:57,548
本気で狂えるくらいの愛しさが
A love so deep that it could make me go crazy...

756
00:55:57,548 --> 00:55:59,248
美しいでしょ
...is beautiful, isn't it?

757
00:55:59,248 --> 00:56:02,748
Get get get on! Get on chu!

758
00:56:02,748 --> 00:56:04,848
Get get get on! Get get get on! Get on chu!

759
00:56:04,848 --> 00:56:05,748
せーの
Ready, set...

760
00:56:05,748 --> 00:56:08,748
ポン・チー・カン 終わんない
Pon, chi, kan, it won't end!

761
00:56:08,748 --> 00:56:11,548
Get Get Get on chu!

762
00:56:11,548 --> 00:56:14,548
我愛你 無問題
Wo ai ni, mou mantai!

763
00:56:14,548 --> 00:56:18,748
Get Get Get on chu!

764
00:56:23,748 --> 00:56:25,748
わー！やったー！
Wow! We did it!

765
00:56:25,748 --> 00:56:28,548
うまくいったしー！
It went so well!

766
00:56:28,548 --> 00:56:32,748
よかったー！頑張ったね、クロちゃん！
I'm so glad! You did great, Kuro-chan!

767
00:56:32,748 --> 00:56:36,648
楽しかった！ありがとう！
That was so fun! Thank you!

768
00:56:36,748 --> 00:56:40,948
えー、ちょっとね、さよならする前に...
So, um, before we say goodbye...

769
00:56:40,948 --> 00:56:43,548
えーっと、1個お願いしてもいいですか？
Um, can we ask you for one favor?

770
00:56:43,548 --> 00:56:45,248
1個だけだしん？
Just one, shin?

771
00:56:45,248 --> 00:56:46,948
はい、1個だけしん！
Yes, just one, shin!

772
00:56:46,948 --> 00:56:53,548
えっと、フワモコは魔界の番犬で、バウバウをよく言っているんですけど...
Um, FUWAMOCO are demon guard dogs, and we often say "Bau Bau"...

773
00:56:53,548 --> 00:57:00,548
クロちゃん、カメラに向かって、フワモコのように可愛いバウバウをしてもらえますか？
Kuro-chan, can you look at the camera and do a cute "Bau Bau" like FUWAMOCO?

774
00:57:00,548 --> 00:57:02,748
えー！できるかしん？
What! Can I do it, shin?

775
00:57:02,748 --> 00:57:05,248
行くしんよ！
Here we go, shin!

776
00:57:05,248 --> 00:57:07,248
バウ！バウ！
Bau! Bau!

777
00:57:07,248 --> 00:57:10,248
え、それがベスト？
Wait, is that your best?

778
00:57:10,248 --> 00:57:13,948
もう一回！もっとやって！
One more time! Do it more!

779
00:57:13,948 --> 00:57:19,548
バウ！バウ！
Bau! Bau!

780
00:57:19,548 --> 00:57:23,248
実は、もう一個やりたいことがあるんですけど...
Actually, there's one more thing we want to do...

781
00:57:23,248 --> 00:57:24,548
何？
What?

782
00:57:24,548 --> 00:57:30,248
さきほどやりましたけど、フワモコはいつもやってる自己紹介があって...
We did it earlier, but FUWAMOCO has a self-introduction we always do...

783
00:57:30,248 --> 00:57:32,748
できれば、3人で一緒にやりたいです！
If possible, we'd like to do it together with all three of us!

784
00:57:32,748 --> 00:57:36,248
あ、あれ可愛かったから、やりたい！クロちゃんも！
Oh, that was cute, I want to do it too!

785
00:57:36,248 --> 00:57:38,248
イェーイ！じゃあ行きますよ！
Yay! Here we go then!

786
00:57:38,248 --> 00:57:39,748
オッケー！
Okay!

787
00:57:39,748 --> 00:57:42,248
凍らすよ！フワワだよ！
I'll freeze you! I'm Fuwawa!

788
00:57:42,248 --> 00:57:45,248
わー！フワワじゃないよ！クロちゃんだよ！
Wah! I'm not Fuwawa! I'm Kuro-chan!

789
00:57:45,248 --> 00:57:48,748
あっ、クロちゃんじゃないよ！モココだよ！
Ah, it's not Kuro-chan! I'm Mococo!

790
00:57:48,748 --> 00:57:51,248
3人合わせて...
And together we are...

791
00:57:51,248 --> 00:57:54,248
いやいやいや！バウバウ！
No, no, no! Bau Bau!

792
00:57:54,248 --> 00:57:58,248
ちょっとちょっと、クロちゃん！
Wait a minute, Kuro-chan!

793
00:57:58,248 --> 00:58:02,748
もう、嘘とかつくなよね！
Don't lie to us anymore!

794
00:58:02,748 --> 00:58:06,248
モココ、パンチしちゃう！
Mococo's gonna punch you!

795
00:58:06,248 --> 00:58:10,248
えー！痛い痛い痛い！
Ah! It hurts, it hurts, it hurts!

796
00:58:10,248 --> 00:58:12,248
救急車、1台...
An ambulance, please...

797
00:58:12,248 --> 00:58:15,248
いらないよ、もう嘘！
No need! No more lies!

798
00:58:15,248 --> 00:58:18,248
プンプン！
Pout, pout!

799
00:58:18,248 --> 00:58:21,248
落ち着いて、落ち着いて！
Calm down, calm down!

800
00:58:21,248 --> 00:58:24,248
大丈夫、モコちゃん、大丈夫。
It's okay, Moco-chan, it's okay.

801
00:58:24,248 --> 00:58:31,748
クロちゃんは、これからもみんなをいっぱい笑顔にして、素敵なアイドルになってくださいね！
Kuro-chan, please keep making everyone smile and become a wonderful idol!

802
00:58:31,748 --> 00:58:34,248
バウバウ！
Bau Bau!

803
00:58:34,248 --> 00:58:39,248
じゃあ、モコちゃん、最後にクロちゃんにハイタッチしてお別れしようね。
Well, Moco-chan, let's end with a high-five for Kuro-chan and say goodbye.

804
00:58:39,248 --> 00:58:42,748
仲直り、仲直り？
Reconciliation, reconciliation?

805
00:58:42,748 --> 00:58:45,748
せーの、ハイタッチ！ハイタッチ！
Ready, high-five! High-five!

806
00:58:45,748 --> 00:58:51,748
ほらほら！やってみて、やってみて！
Come on! Give it a try, give it a try!

807
00:58:51,748 --> 00:58:55,248
デコピン！
Flick!

808
00:58:55,248 --> 00:58:59,748
痛っ！なんで？ちょっと！ひどくない？
Ouch! Why?! Hey! Isn't that mean?

809
00:58:59,748 --> 00:59:04,748
けど、フワモコちゃん、本当に、お誕生日おめでとうございます！
But FUWAMOCO, truly, happy birthday!

810
00:59:04,748 --> 00:59:07,748
ありがとう！ありがとうしん！
Thank you! Thank you, shin!

811
00:59:07,748 --> 00:59:12,748
きゅんからの、バッキュン！おめでとうハート！
Kyun and then... bam! Happy birthday heart!

812
00:59:12,748 --> 00:59:14,748
バウバウ！レッツゴーン！
Bau Bau! Let's go-n!

813
00:59:14,748 --> 00:59:29,248
わあ！すごーい！花火だー！たまやー！
Wow! Amazing! Fireworks! Tamaya!

814
00:59:29,748 --> 00:59:32,748
Wow! That was so nice!

815
00:59:32,748 --> 00:59:36,248
Things got really crazy, but I'm glad that you are happy!

816
00:59:36,748 --> 00:59:40,748
なんか、クロちゃん凄すぎて、分かんなくなってきたかも！
Like, Kuro-chan was so incredible, I think I'm starting to lose track of what's happening!

817
00:59:40,748 --> 00:59:44,248
But we still have one more, one more very exciting thing to share with you!

818
00:59:44,248 --> 00:59:48,748
Yes! まだまだ楽しみがあるよ！
Yes! We still have more fun in store!

819
00:59:48,748 --> 00:59:51,748
Maybe... what is it? Can you guess what it is?

820
00:59:51,748 --> 00:59:56,748
何かな？何かな？
What could it be? What could it be?

821
00:59:56,748 --> 01:00:01,748
Well, FUWAMOCO are at our first anniversary!

822
01:00:01,529 --> 01:00:04,029
We were able to release our very first original song!

823
01:00:04,029 --> 01:00:06,029
Going to be a ballad!

824
01:00:06,029 --> 01:00:10,029
And then for our second anniversary, we were able to release Lifetime Showtime!

825
01:00:10,029 --> 01:00:14,529
Our original song that's been on with us along this journey!

826
01:00:14,529 --> 01:00:17,029
Yeah, very special song.

827
01:00:17,029 --> 01:00:22,029
And you know, for FuwaMoco, singing and dancing is something that means so much to us!

828
01:00:22,029 --> 01:00:25,529
Yeah, music! And Ruffians...

829
01:00:25,529 --> 01:00:29,529
...might have heard that you'd like to hear more from us, too, right?

830
01:00:29,529 --> 01:00:33,029
Yeah! Yeah! Yeah! What do you think?

831
01:00:33,029 --> 01:00:35,529
Well...

832
01:00:35,529 --> 01:00:38,029
Our announcement is...

833
01:00:38,029 --> 01:00:41,029
Drumroll! Okay, drumroll, Ruffians!

834
01:00:41,029 --> 01:00:46,029
Prrrrrrrrrr...

835
01:00:46,529 --> 01:00:51,529
A new original song!

836
01:00:51,529 --> 01:00:54,029
Yes! Original song!

837
01:00:54,529 --> 01:00:57,029
And this song, it's extra special!

838
01:00:57,029 --> 01:01:03,529
It's written by none other than the legendary rock idol song composer, Matsukuma Kenta-san!

839
01:01:03,529 --> 01:01:07,029
Who works with many famous idol groups, wow!

840
01:01:07,029 --> 01:01:13,529
Also written music for the idol group that Kuro-chan produces, MAMESHiBA NO TAiG0!

841
01:01:13,529 --> 01:01:17,029
But Ruffians, you might be a little bit surprised, okay?

842
01:01:17,529 --> 01:01:20,029
So get ready!

843
01:01:20,529 --> 01:01:22,529
Ruffians... with this song...

844
01:01:22,529 --> 01:01:27,029
...we'd like to express our roughest feelings as demon dogs.

845
01:01:30,029 --> 01:01:32,029
DEMON'S RESiDENCE.

846
01:01:46,529 --> 01:01:55,529
DEMON'S RESIDENCE / 作詞：海野水玉 作曲：松隈ケンタ 編編：SCRAMBLES
[Title: DEMON'S RESIDENCE / Lyrics: Mizutama Umino, Music: Kenta Matsukuma, Arrangement: SCRAMBLES]

847
01:01:56,529 --> 01:02:01,529
「相棒、どこへ行こうか」 ネオンの脇を抜け
"Buddy, where shall we go?" Slipping past the neon lights

848
01:02:01,529 --> 01:02:06,029
バブルガムがはじけたら let's go
When the bubblegum pops, let's go

849
01:02:06,529 --> 01:02:11,029
最低な夜を潜って 僕らは群れをなす
Slinking through this wretched night, we run in a pack

850
01:02:11,029 --> 01:02:16,029
「あの頃よりもマシだね」 my way
"Better than back then, huh?" my way

851
01:02:16,529 --> 01:02:21,029
「不完全なんです」 首輪をつけた
"It's incomplete," wearing a collar

852
01:02:21,029 --> 01:02:26,529
良い子なんかじゃもうイヤ Ah!!
I'm already fed up with being a good girl, ah!

853
01:02:26,529 --> 01:02:29,529
DEMON'S RESIDENCE 噛みついていけ
DEMON'S RESIDENCE, bite down!

854
01:02:29,529 --> 01:02:32,029
この街は檻のようで
This city is like a cage

855
01:02:32,029 --> 01:02:34,529
気分はどうだい 泣いているのかい
How do you feel? Are you crying?

856
01:02:34,529 --> 01:02:39,029
鎖をちぎって 叫んでいたいんだ stray dogs
Rip the chains apart, I want to keep screaming, stray dogs

857
01:02:39,529 --> 01:02:42,029
彼方へと 飛ぶ鳥を
Flying towards the distant horizon...

858
01:02:42,029 --> 01:02:44,529
見上げるだけかい それでいいのかい
Is that all you do? Is that enough?

859
01:02:44,529 --> 01:02:49,529
燃えるなら ほら青く
If you're going to burn, then look, burn blue

860
01:02:57,529 --> 01:03:02,029
「説教なんかいらない」 スプレー缶振って
"I don't need any lectures," shaking a spray paint can

861
01:03:02,029 --> 01:03:07,029
イタズラ書きで彩る runway
Coloring the runway with graffiti

862
01:03:07,529 --> 01:03:12,029
愛情なんか coin toss 誰に bet するのか
Love is just a coin toss, who are you going to bet on?

863
01:03:12,029 --> 01:03:17,029
不確定要素ばかりね lonely
It's just full of uncertain factors, lonely

864
01:03:17,529 --> 01:03:22,529
二人でひとつと決めた
We decided on one for the two of us

865
01:03:23,529 --> 01:03:28,029
あの目を忘れない Ah!!
I won't forget those eyes, ah!

866
01:03:28,029 --> 01:03:30,529
DEMON'S RESIDENCE 満天の空
DEMON'S RESIDENCE, a sky full of stars

867
01:03:30,529 --> 01:03:33,029
あの星がひどく不快で
That star is terribly unpleasant

868
01:03:33,029 --> 01:03:35,029
勝利は上々だ 味はするのかい
Victory is splendid, can you taste it?

869
01:03:35,529 --> 01:03:40,029
鎖を噛んで 唸っていたいんだ stray dogs 僕ら
Biting the chains, I want to keep growling, stray dogs, us

870
01:03:41,029 --> 01:03:43,529
宇宙さえも撃ち落として
Shooting down even the universe

871
01:03:43,529 --> 01:03:46,029
見下ろす奈落 ビルは輝く
Looking down at the abyss, the buildings shine

872
01:03:46,029 --> 01:03:51,529
LOL Now I am free!!

873
01:04:04,029 --> 01:04:13,529
Woah-oh-oh-oh Woah-oh-oh Woah-oh-oh-oh Woah-oh-oh...

874
01:04:14,529 --> 01:04:19,029
孤独を分け合い食べた
Sharing and eating our loneliness

875
01:04:19,529 --> 01:04:24,029
あの日を忘れない Ah!!
I won't forget that day, ah!

876
01:04:24,529 --> 01:04:27,029
夜を睨んだ stray dogs そうだ
Staring at the night, stray dogs, that's right

877
01:04:27,029 --> 01:04:29,529
怪物は世界のほうさ
The monster is the world itself

878
01:04:29,529 --> 01:04:32,029
抜け出せるのかい 足は動くかい
Can you escape? Can your legs move?

879
01:04:32,029 --> 01:04:34,529
走るなら今
If you're going to run, do it now

880
01:04:34,529 --> 01:04:37,029
DEMON'S RESIDENCE stray dogs 僕ら
DEMON'S RESIDENCE, stray dogs, us

881
01:04:37,029 --> 01:04:39,529
この街を駆け抜けて行け
Run through this city

882
01:04:39,529 --> 01:04:42,029
地獄の果てに何が見えるかい
What can you see at the end of hell?

883
01:04:42,529 --> 01:04:47,029
鎖をちぎって 叫んでいたいんだ stray dogs 僕ら
Rip the chains apart, I want to keep screaming, stray dogs, us

884
01:04:47,529 --> 01:04:49,529
この街は檻のようで
This city is like a cage

885
01:04:49,529 --> 01:04:52,029
君ならどうだい 共に駆けるかい
How about you? Will you run with me?

886
01:04:52,529 --> 01:04:55,029
夜明けが合図だ
Dawn is the signal...

887
01:04:55,529 --> 01:05:00,029
行こう
Let's go!

888
01:05:51,684 --> 01:05:53,184
Bau bau!

889
01:05:53,584 --> 01:05:57,284
Thank you for always being here for us!

890
01:05:58,684 --> 01:05:59,884
Please listen to...

891
01:05:59,984 --> 01:06:02,184
side by side!

892
01:06:04,584 --> 01:06:08,984
Finally we made it through but not without some tears

893
01:06:12,084 --> 01:06:17,384
With the help of friends so true we faced all of our fears

894
01:06:19,584 --> 01:06:23,084
Now we're here to celebrate all that we have done

895
01:06:26,584 --> 01:06:30,484
I can feel it's more than just a game of fate

896
01:06:30,584 --> 01:06:33,984
'cause our stories have just begun

897
01:06:35,184 --> 01:06:38,584
Hand in hand we're not waiting on tomorrow

898
01:06:38,784 --> 01:06:42,684
From now on it's the heart that we will follow

899
01:06:43,084 --> 01:06:46,484
We'll move on passed the heartbreak and the sorrow if you

900
01:06:46,584 --> 01:06:50,084
Stay by my side

901
01:06:50,584 --> 01:06:53,984
Dancing harmonies feeding the music

902
01:06:53,984 --> 01:06:57,384
as we come alive, and sparks ignite

903
01:06:57,984 --> 01:07:01,584
We're making memories everyday underneath

904
01:07:01,584 --> 01:07:05,284
the summer sky and through the night

905
01:07:05,784 --> 01:07:09,384
We're singing melodies every time we hear music

906
01:07:09,584 --> 01:07:13,284
from inside as hearts collide

907
01:07:13,584 --> 01:07:17,084
Bringing out the best in each other

908
01:07:17,184 --> 01:07:20,984
now we're feeling free like we're meant to be

909
01:07:21,384 --> 01:07:25,084
Even though there's been rough times where nobody wanted us,

910
01:07:25,184 --> 01:07:28,384
we kept going, and we kept dreaming,

911
01:07:30,084 --> 01:07:31,584
now we are here,

912
01:07:31,584 --> 01:07:33,084
we're not alone anymore!

913
01:07:33,184 --> 01:07:34,784
We'll be here together. We have smiles to protect!

914
01:07:34,884 --> 01:07:36,584
C'mon, let's go!

915
01:07:36,584 --> 01:07:39,784
Dancing harmonies feeding the music

916
01:07:39,784 --> 01:07:43,584
as we come alive, and sparks ignite

917
01:07:43,984 --> 01:07:47,584
We're making memories everyday underneath

918
01:07:47,584 --> 01:07:51,284
the summer sky and through the night

919
01:07:51,584 --> 01:07:55,184
We're singing melodies every time we hear music

920
01:07:55,184 --> 01:07:59,184
from inside as hearts collide

921
01:07:59,284 --> 01:08:03,084
Bringing out the best in each other

922
01:08:03,184 --> 01:08:07,084
now we're feeling free like we're meant to be

923
01:08:07,384 --> 01:08:14,184
Nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya

924
01:08:14,384 --> 01:08:20,984
Nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya

925
01:08:21,184 --> 01:08:29,584
Nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya

926
01:08:29,784 --> 01:08:38,584
Nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya nya

927
01:08:39,084 --> 01:08:41,084
Bau bau!

928
01:08:45,784 --> 01:08:47,884
Thank you for the encore, Ruffians!

929
01:08:47,984 --> 01:08:50,584
That was side by side!

930
01:08:50,584 --> 01:08:52,584
Bau bau!

931
01:08:52,884 --> 01:08:58,084
We're really happy to sing side by side for you for the first time live today!

932
01:08:58,184 --> 01:09:00,584
Yeah! 初披露できてとっても嬉しかったです！
Yeah! We are so happy we got to perform it live for the first time!

933
01:09:00,784 --> 01:09:03,584
Yeah, side by side is a song made by Aiobahn-san,

934
01:09:03,684 --> 01:09:06,984
but also between FuwaMoco!

935
01:09:07,084 --> 01:09:09,084
Yeah, it is!

936
01:09:09,184 --> 01:09:12,084
We know it's a song that you love a lot,

937
01:09:12,184 --> 01:09:16,084
but we also do because it's very special to us

938
01:09:16,184 --> 01:09:20,084
since it's the ending theme for a visual novel that we care about...

939
01:09:20,384 --> 01:09:22,084
Nekopara!

940
01:09:22,084 --> 01:09:24,084
Nekopara! Bau bau!

941
01:09:24,584 --> 01:09:30,584
And with this song, our dream of singing the opening or ending theme for a visual novel came true!

942
01:09:30,584 --> 01:09:32,384
Yeah!

943
01:09:32,384 --> 01:09:38,584
そう、この曲で、Fuwamocoの夢、美少女ゲームの主題歌を歌うことが叶いました！
That's right, with this song, FuwaMoco's dream of singing the theme song for a bishojo game has come true!

944
01:09:38,684 --> 01:09:41,584
It came true! Thank you! Thank you!

945
01:09:41,584 --> 01:09:43,084
ありがとう！
Thank you!

946
01:09:43,084 --> 01:09:47,584
And thank you so much for joining us for a special day again this year.

947
01:09:47,684 --> 01:09:50,584
It's been a dream, Ruffians!

948
01:09:50,684 --> 01:09:54,584
And we know it's all because of you that we're able to be here

949
01:09:54,684 --> 01:09:57,584
and do all the amazing things that we do, so thank you.

950
01:09:57,684 --> 01:09:59,084
Thank you!

951
01:09:59,184 --> 01:10:00,584
It's sad to say, but...

952
01:10:00,965 --> 01:10:03,565
あ！次の歌は…最後の歌です。
Ah! This next song... is our last song.

953
01:10:03,965 --> 01:10:05,165
えー！
Aw...

954
01:10:05,365 --> 01:10:09,465
でも、特別だよ！
But, you know... it's a very special one.

955
01:10:09,765 --> 01:10:15,465
フワモコは魔界の番犬として、みんなの笑顔を守るためにここにいるんだよね！
You know, FUWAMOCO, as demon guard dogs, we're here to protect your smile, right?

956
01:10:15,765 --> 01:10:17,765
これからもそうしていくよ。笑顔を守るために！
We will continue to do that. To protect your smile!

957
01:10:17,965 --> 01:10:19,965
アイドルとして、全力でね！
Yeah, doing our all as idols!

958
01:10:20,265 --> 01:10:24,465
それに、ふわふわでもこもこな魂もね！
And just as our fluffy and fuzzy souls, too!

959
01:10:25,465 --> 01:10:28,965
何千年も、何万年も、魔界の犬の歳としてここに居続けるよ！
We'll continue to be here for thousands and thousands of demon dog years.

960
01:10:29,465 --> 01:10:34,265
毎日が当たり前じゃないってことを思い出しながらね。
All while remembering that everyday isn't given.

961
01:10:34,665 --> 01:10:37,465
当たり前なことなんて何一つないからね。
We don't take anything for granted.

962
01:10:37,965 --> 01:10:43,965
だから落ち込んだ時は、私たちがいつでもここで応援してるって思い出してね！
And you know, when you're down, we hope you'll remember that we're always here cheering you on, okay?

963
01:10:44,065 --> 01:10:45,965
うん！ラフィアンズを全力で応援するよ！
Yes! We'll cheer you on, Ruffians!

964
01:10:46,265 --> 01:10:49,965
だから、今日の最後の曲の歌詞を、よーく聴いててね！
So, please listen closely to the lyrics of our last song for today!

965
01:11:04,965 --> 01:11:06,965
明日も
May tomorrow...

966
01:11:07,065 --> 01:11:08,465
明後日も
...and the day after too...

967
01:11:08,565 --> 01:11:11,465
あなたが笑ってますように
...I hope you will be laughing...

968
01:11:11,565 --> 01:11:13,765
ずっと
...forever.

969
01:11:13,865 --> 01:11:16,965
Lala...

970
01:11:18,965 --> 01:11:22,765
ラフィアンズ、今日は私たちの誕生日を一緒に過ごしてくれて本当にありがとう！
Thank you so much Ruffians for spending our birthday with us today!

971
01:11:22,965 --> 01:11:26,765
辛い時はいつでもこの歌を思い出して、私たちがそばにいることを忘れないでね。
Please think of this song whenever things are rough, and know that we'll be here.

972
01:11:26,965 --> 01:11:28,965
この最後の歌をみんなに贈ります。
This last song is for you.

973
01:11:29,065 --> 01:11:31,465
「Wishful Garnet」！
Wishful Garnet!

974
01:11:32,965 --> 01:11:38,465
過去を振り返ると 思い出す
When I look back at the past, I remember

975
01:11:38,565 --> 01:11:44,865
ガーネットの空 溢れてく 光
The light overflowing from the garnet sky

976
01:11:44,965 --> 01:11:49,465
この瞳に映し出された あの日は
The day reflected in these eyes of mine

977
01:11:49,965 --> 01:11:54,965
美しく 揺れる
Sways beautifully

978
01:11:56,165 --> 01:11:57,465
What do you think?

979
01:11:57,565 --> 01:12:01,965
紅く 滲んだ空に
To the sky tinged with red...

980
01:12:02,065 --> 01:12:07,965
願いました どうかこの願い
...I made a wish, please let this wish...

981
01:12:08,065 --> 01:12:10,465
届けてください
...reach you.

982
01:12:10,965 --> 01:12:12,765
明日も
May tomorrow...

983
01:12:12,865 --> 01:12:14,165
明後日も
...and the day after too...

984
01:12:14,265 --> 01:12:16,465
あなたが笑ってますように
...I hope you will be laughing.

985
01:12:16,765 --> 01:12:19,465
離れ離れになっても
Even if we are apart...

986
01:12:19,765 --> 01:12:22,965
前を向けますように
...I hope you can keep looking forward.

987
01:12:23,065 --> 01:12:25,765
あなたを縛る鎖を
The chains that bind you...

988
01:12:25,865 --> 01:12:28,965
わたしが壊してあげる
...I will break them for you.

989
01:12:29,165 --> 01:12:31,465
もう負けないで
Do not give up...

990
01:12:31,565 --> 01:12:34,265
進むこと
...keep moving forward.

991
01:12:34,365 --> 01:12:38,965
いつでもそばにいるから
Because I will always be by your side.

992
01:15:07,020 --> 01:15:09,520
離れ離れになっても
Even if we are separated,

993
01:15:09,520 --> 01:15:12,520
前を向けますように
I hope you can keep facing forward.

994
01:15:12,520 --> 01:15:15,520
あなたを縛る鎖を
I will break the chains

995
01:15:15,520 --> 01:15:18,520
わたしが壊してあげる
that bind you.

996
01:15:18,520 --> 01:15:24,020
もう負けないで進むこと
Don't give up, keep moving forward,

997
01:15:24,020 --> 01:15:26,520
いつでもそばに
because I will always

998
01:15:26,520 --> 01:15:29,520
あなたのそばに
be by your side,

999
01:15:29,520 --> 01:15:36,020
わたしはいつもいるから
here for you.

1000
01:15:36,020 --> 01:15:41,020
Lalala...

1001
01:15:41,020 --> 01:15:48,020
Yeah... yeah...

1002
01:16:11,520 --> 01:16:13,020
Bau bau!

1003
01:16:13,020 --> 01:16:15,520
Thank you so much, Ruffians!

1004
01:16:15,520 --> 01:16:19,520
We'll see you soon at our encore live in membership, okay?

1005
01:16:19,520 --> 01:16:21,520
Bau bau!

